1
00:00:02,424 --> 00:00:04,333
I like you.

2
00:00:13,375 --> 00:00:15,523
Do you want to go out with me?

3
00:00:16,834 --> 00:00:19,694
He'd probably say no.

4
00:00:23,584 --> 00:00:25,859
I want us to be something special.

5
00:00:25,859 --> 00:00:29,363
You're special... to me.

6
00:00:29,363 --> 00:00:32,995
Let's make it... official today.

7
00:00:36,245 --> 00:00:39,542
This is all wrong. It sounds too casual.

8
00:00:39,542 --> 00:00:41,662
What should I do?

9
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:46,128
A letter.

10
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:01,944
But how am I supposed to give this to him?

11
00:01:03,522 --> 00:01:06,205
[Let's meet outside next time]

12
00:01:10,946 --> 00:01:13,842
[Best date spots in Seoul]

13
00:01:29,924 --> 00:01:31,685
You're here early.

14
00:01:38,250 --> 00:01:39,766
Want to go here today?

15
00:01:39,766 --> 00:01:41,712
It's supposed to be really beautiful here.

16
00:01:42,918 --> 00:01:44,771
I can't.

17
00:01:44,771 --> 00:01:46,292
Why not?

18
00:01:46,292 --> 00:01:48,402
I've got things to do.

19
00:01:49,459 --> 00:01:52,161
- Then how about tomorrow?
- I'm busy.

20
00:01:57,751 --> 00:01:59,475
What do I do?

21
00:02:10,918 --> 00:02:12,167
Soo An,

22
00:02:12,167 --> 00:02:14,642
how are you feeling about today's shoot?

23
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,577
Hey.

24
00:02:21,542 --> 00:02:23,991
How are you feeling about today's shoot?

25
00:02:27,792 --> 00:02:29,209
Good.

26
00:02:29,209 --> 00:02:30,484
It's been a while since our last shoot,

27
00:02:30,484 --> 00:02:33,661
so I'm a little nervous
and excited at the same time.

28
00:02:34,410 --> 00:02:36,240
Just trust me and do what I say for today.

29
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,534
I've prepared everything.

30
00:02:38,534 --> 00:02:42,083
Sounds like you put in a lot of work.
I'll make sure to do my best, too.

31
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:43,121
Hey guys!

32
00:02:43,121 --> 00:02:46,597
Stay tuned for our Reels
and behind-the-scenes today!

33
00:02:46,597 --> 00:02:49,105
Get ready for some awesome footage!

34
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:53,931
Anyway, I skipped breakfast today,
so I'm starving.

35
00:03:00,637 --> 00:03:02,683
Oh, look! Snacks!

36
00:03:02,683 --> 00:03:05,417
Looks like Soo An packed these for us.

37
00:03:05,417 --> 00:03:07,281
He's so thoughtful.

38
00:03:08,292 --> 00:03:12,192
But I can't really eat right now
since I'm driving.

39
00:03:12,192 --> 00:03:15,445
You go ahead and eat.

40
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:18,042
I don't want you going hungry.

41
00:03:18,042 --> 00:03:19,497
What's that?

42
00:03:19,497 --> 00:03:21,850
You feel bad eating by yourself?

43
00:03:24,834 --> 00:03:26,233
Ah.

44
00:03:28,876 --> 00:03:30,125
Come on.

45
00:03:30,125 --> 00:03:31,281
Ah.

46
00:03:31,281 --> 00:03:33,125
Unbelievable.

47
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:41,850
This is good.

48
00:03:51,398 --> 00:03:54,026
I made sure Hyun Jae had enough to eat.

49
00:03:54,026 --> 00:03:56,108
Tastes good, doesn't it?

50
00:03:56,959 --> 00:03:58,497
Yeah.

51
00:04:11,043 --> 00:04:12,806
Khun!

52
00:04:17,257 --> 00:04:20,385
[To Khun]

53
00:04:29,603 --> 00:04:32,083
I'll try harder next time.

54
00:04:32,083 --> 00:04:33,961
I'm so sorry.

55
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,740
Darn it...

56
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:44,292
Soo An is never around
when I actually need him.

57
00:04:44,292 --> 00:04:46,294
Where is he?

58
00:04:49,459 --> 00:04:51,766
Are you looking for something?

59
00:05:07,224 --> 00:05:09,876
The mountains are definitely better
than the beach.

60
00:05:09,876 --> 00:05:11,925
The air up here is totally different.

61
00:05:13,146 --> 00:05:14,591
Right?

62
00:05:14,591 --> 00:05:18,311
You're right. It feels great
to get out of the practice room for once.

63
00:05:18,311 --> 00:05:20,074
This is amazing.

64
00:05:23,292 --> 00:05:25,292
Ta-da!

65
00:05:25,292 --> 00:05:27,020
Let's dig in.

66
00:05:27,709 --> 00:05:29,219
Open up.

67
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,779
You eat it.

68
00:05:35,751 --> 00:05:37,292
Open up.

69
00:05:52,125 --> 00:05:55,137
We came all the way out here.
Let's have some fun first.

70
00:05:55,137 --> 00:05:56,918
I'm good.

71
00:06:22,083 --> 00:06:23,619
Hey.

72
00:06:26,667 --> 00:06:28,680
- Come on in!
- Stop it!

73
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,795
Let's just have some fun!

74
00:06:30,795 --> 00:06:32,017
Come play with me!

75
00:06:32,017 --> 00:06:33,627
Come on in!

76
00:06:37,876 --> 00:06:39,598
Fine, then.

77
00:06:53,539 --> 00:06:56,423
- Hey, what are you doing?
- I told you to get in.

78
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:51,680
- Khun!
- Khun!

79
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:54,474
- Khun.
- Khun.

80
00:07:54,474 --> 00:07:57,769
- Please accept this.
- Khun.

81
00:07:57,769 --> 00:07:59,268
Please accept this.

82
00:08:00,564 --> 00:08:04,044
[To Khun]

83
00:08:08,238 --> 00:08:11,091
[We will always be together]

84
00:08:23,754 --> 00:08:24,630
- Khun!
- Khun!

85
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,764
- Please accept this.
- Khun.

86
00:09:09,375 --> 00:09:11,570
Well, there goes my surprise.

87
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:18,612
Here, take this.

88
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,573
- Khun.
- There he is!

89
00:09:32,573 --> 00:09:34,449
Get out of here. I'll hold them off.

90
00:09:34,449 --> 00:09:36,260
Khun!

91
00:09:57,598 --> 00:09:59,914
Remember the survival show?

92
00:10:02,083 --> 00:10:03,630
Of course I do.

93
00:10:05,512 --> 00:10:07,357
We used to...

94
00:10:07,357 --> 00:10:10,243
do all kinds of stuff in front of the camera.

95
00:10:11,236 --> 00:10:12,971
Yeah, we did.

96
00:10:15,918 --> 00:10:17,565
Hey.

97
00:10:21,706 --> 00:10:23,471
Everything I did then...

98
00:10:23,471 --> 00:10:25,800
I meant all of it.

99
00:10:27,125 --> 00:10:28,697
Me too.

100
00:10:43,459 --> 00:10:45,106
Open up.

101
00:10:45,959 --> 00:10:48,232
- Right?
- You're right.

102
00:10:48,232 --> 00:10:50,400
I meant it all.

103
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,022
Me too.

104
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:03,257
But just so you know...

105
00:11:06,083 --> 00:11:08,791
I didn't hit record today.

106
00:11:19,137 --> 00:11:20,721
I know.

107
00:11:36,167 --> 00:11:38,426
Hey, since when?

108
00:11:38,426 --> 00:11:40,249
Hey, Yoon Soo An!

109
00:11:51,503 --> 00:11:54,543
[To Khun]

110
00:12:15,777 --> 00:12:17,292
Khun!

111
00:12:17,292 --> 00:12:21,825
I feel a little shy
now that I'm actually writing this down.

112
00:12:21,825 --> 00:12:25,287
But at the same time, writing your name out

113
00:12:25,287 --> 00:12:27,456
gave me butterflies.

114
00:12:27,456 --> 00:12:31,626
And just thinking about you right now is
making me nervous all over again.

115
00:12:31,626 --> 00:12:35,167
I'm also wondering how you'll react to this.

116
00:12:35,167 --> 00:12:40,219
It's amazing how one person can make me
feel so many different things.

117
00:12:40,219 --> 00:12:42,804
Every new emotion I feel each day always

118
00:12:42,804 --> 00:12:44,640
leads back to you, Khun.

119
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:46,350
Actually, no.

120
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:49,933
Out of everything, there's only one thing
I'm absolutely sure of.

121
00:12:49,933 --> 00:12:54,092
[Jae Min]
Khun, I like you.

122
00:13:04,751 --> 00:13:07,793
All right, everyone. We'll start
practicing with this demo track for now.

123
00:13:07,793 --> 00:13:09,427
Anyone have any thoughts on this?

124
00:13:09,427 --> 00:13:10,927
It hits you the second you hear it, right?

125
00:13:10,927 --> 00:13:12,607
That's your song.

126
00:13:12,607 --> 00:13:14,719
It's like it was written specifically for you.

127
00:13:15,334 --> 00:13:16,921
When did you figure it out?

128
00:13:16,921 --> 00:13:20,125
- How did you know?
- Shut up.

129
00:13:20,125 --> 00:13:23,792
Then can I give you my answer now?

130
00:13:23,792 --> 00:13:25,848
What's going on? What's with them?

131
00:13:25,848 --> 00:13:27,653
Jae Min!

132
00:13:28,334 --> 00:13:31,251
Hey, Jae Min.

